README.md
     1‚Üí# humanize
    12‚ÜíThis modest package contains various common humanization utilities, like turning a
    13‚Üínumber into a fuzzy human-readable duration ("3 minutes ago") or into a human-readable
    14‚Üísize or throughput. It is localized to:
    15‚Üí
    16‚Üí- Arabic
    17‚Üí- Basque
    18‚Üí- Bengali
    19‚Üí- Brazilian Portuguese
    20‚Üí- Catalan
    21‚Üí- Danish
    22‚Üí- Dutch
    23‚Üí- Esperanto
    24‚Üí- European Portuguese
    25‚Üí- Finnish
    26‚Üí- French
    27‚Üí- German
    28‚Üí- Greek
    29‚Üí- Hebrew
    30‚Üí- Indonesian
    31‚Üí- Italian
    32‚Üí- Japanese
    33‚Üí- Klingon
    34‚Üí- Korean
    35‚Üí- Norwegian
    36‚Üí- Persian
    37‚Üí- Polish
    38‚Üí- Russian
    39‚Üí- Simplified Chinese
    40‚Üí- Slovak
    41‚Üí- Slovenian
    42‚Üí- Spanish
    43‚Üí- Swedish
    44‚Üí- Turkish
    45‚Üí- Ukrainian
    46‚Üí- Uzbek
    47‚Üí- Vietnamese
    48‚Üí
    49‚Üí## API reference
    51‚Üí[https://humanize.readthedocs.io](https://humanize.readthedocs.io/)
    52‚Üí
    53‚Üí<!-- usage-start -->
    54‚Üí
    55‚Üí## Installation
    57‚Üí### From PyPI
    59‚Üí```bash
    60‚Üípython3 -m pip install --upgrade humanize
    61‚Üí```
    62‚Üí
    63‚Üí### From source
    65‚Üí```bash
    66‚Üígit clone https://github.com/python-humanize/humanize
    67‚Üícd humanize
    68‚Üípython3 -m pip install -e .
    69‚Üí```
    70‚Üí
    71‚Üí## Usage
    73‚Üí### Integer humanization
    75‚Üí```pycon
    76‚Üí>>> import humanize
    77‚Üí>>> humanize.intcomma(12345)
    78‚Üí'12,345'
    79‚Üí>>> humanize.intword(123455913)
    80‚Üí'123.5 million'
    81‚Üí>>> humanize.intword(12345591313)
    82‚Üí'12.3 billion'
    83‚Üí>>> humanize.apnumber(4)
    84‚Üí'four'
    85‚Üí>>> humanize.apnumber(41)
    86‚Üí'41'
    87‚Üí```
    88‚Üí
    89‚Üí### Date & time humanization
    91‚Üí```pycon
    92‚Üí>>> import humanize
    93‚Üí>>> import datetime as dt
    94‚Üí>>> humanize.naturalday(dt.datetime.now())
    95‚Üí'today'
    96‚Üí>>> humanize.naturaldelta(dt.timedelta(seconds=1001))
    97‚Üí'16 minutes'
    98‚Üí>>> humanize.naturalday(dt.datetime.now() - dt.timedelta(days=1))
    99‚Üí'yesterday'
   100‚Üí>>> humanize.naturalday(dt.date(2007, 6, 5))
   101‚Üí'Jun 05'
   102‚Üí>>> humanize.naturaldate(dt.date(2007, 6, 5))
   103‚Üí'Jun 05 2007'
   104‚Üí>>> humanize.naturaltime(dt.datetime.now() - dt.timedelta(seconds=1))
   105‚Üí'a second ago'
   106‚Üí>>> humanize.naturaltime(dt.datetime.now() - dt.timedelta(seconds=3600))
   107‚Üí'an hour ago'
   108‚Üí```
   109‚Üí
   110‚Üí### Precise time delta
   112‚Üí```pycon
   113‚Üí>>> import humanize
   114‚Üí>>> import datetime as dt
   115‚Üí>>> delta = dt.timedelta(seconds=3633, days=2, microseconds=123000)
   116‚Üí>>> humanize.precisedelta(delta)
   117‚Üí'2 days, 1 hour and 33.12 seconds'
   118‚Üí>>> humanize.precisedelta(delta, minimum_unit="microseconds")
   119‚Üí'2 days, 1 hour, 33 seconds and 123 milliseconds'
   120‚Üí>>> humanize.precisedelta(delta, suppress=["days"], format="%0.4f")
   121‚Üí'49 hours and 33.1230 seconds'
   122‚Üí```
   123‚Üí
   124‚Üí#### Smaller units
   126‚ÜíIf seconds are too large, set `minimum_unit` to milliseconds or microseconds:
   127‚Üí
   128‚Üí```pycon
   129‚Üí>>> import humanize
   130‚Üí>>> import datetime as dt
   131‚Üí>>> humanize.naturaldelta(dt.timedelta(seconds=2))
   132‚Üí'2 seconds'
   133‚Üí```
   134‚Üí
   135‚Üí```pycon
   136‚Üí>>> delta = dt.timedelta(milliseconds=4)
   137‚Üí>>> humanize.naturaldelta(delta)
   138‚Üí'a moment'
   139‚Üí>>> humanize.naturaldelta(delta, minimum_unit="milliseconds")
   140‚Üí'4 milliseconds'
   141‚Üí>>> humanize.naturaldelta(delta, minimum_unit="microseconds")
   142‚Üí'4 milliseconds'
   143‚Üí```
   144‚Üí
   145‚Üí```pycon
   146‚Üí>>> humanize.naturaltime(delta)
   147‚Üí'now'
   148‚Üí>>> humanize.naturaltime(delta, minimum_unit="milliseconds")
   149‚Üí'4 milliseconds ago'
   150‚Üí>>> humanize.naturaltime(delta, minimum_unit="microseconds")
   151‚Üí'4 milliseconds ago'
   152‚Üí```
   153‚Üí
   154‚Üí### File size humanization
   156‚Üí```pycon
   157‚Üí>>> import humanize
   158‚Üí>>> humanize.naturalsize(1_000_000)
   159‚Üí'1.0 MB'
   160‚Üí>>> humanize.naturalsize(1_000_000, binary=True)
   161‚Üí'976.6 KiB'
   162‚Üí>>> humanize.naturalsize(1_000_000, gnu=True)
   163‚Üí'976.6K'
   164‚Üí```
   165‚Üí
   166‚Üí### Human-readable floating point numbers
   168‚Üí```pycon
   169‚Üí>>> import humanize
   170‚Üí>>> humanize.fractional(1/3)
   171‚Üí'1/3'
   172‚Üí>>> humanize.fractional(1.5)
   173‚Üí'1 1/2'
   174‚Üí>>> humanize.fractional(0.3)
   175‚Üí'3/10'
   176‚Üí>>> humanize.fractional(0.333)
   177‚Üí'333/1000'
   178‚Üí>>> humanize.fractional(1)
   179‚Üí'1'
   180‚Üí```
   181‚Üí
   182‚Üí### Scientific notation
   184‚Üí```pycon
   185‚Üí>>> import humanize
   186‚Üí>>> humanize.scientific(0.3)
   187‚Üí'3.00 x 10‚Åª¬π'
   188‚Üí>>> humanize.scientific(500)
   189‚Üí'5.00 x 10¬≤'
   190‚Üí>>> humanize.scientific("20000")
   191‚Üí'2.00 x 10‚Å¥'
   192‚Üí>>> humanize.scientific(1**10)
   193‚Üí'1.00 x 10‚Å∞'
   194‚Üí>>> humanize.scientific(1**10, precision=1)
   195‚Üí'1.0 x 10‚Å∞'
   196‚Üí>>> humanize.scientific(1**10, precision=0)
   197‚Üí'1 x 10‚Å∞'
   198‚Üí```
   199‚Üí
   200‚Üí## Localization
   202‚ÜíHow to change locale at runtime:
   203‚Üí
   204‚Üí```pycon
   205‚Üí>>> import humanize
   206‚Üí>>> import datetime as dt
   207‚Üí>>> humanize.naturaltime(dt.timedelta(seconds=3))
   208‚Üí'3 seconds ago'
   209‚Üí>>> _t = humanize.i18n.activate("ru_RU")
   210‚Üí>>> humanize.naturaltime(dt.timedelta(seconds=3))
   211‚Üí'3 —Å–µ–∫—É–Ω–¥—ã –Ω–∞–∑–∞–¥'
   212‚Üí>>> humanize.i18n.deactivate()
   213‚Üí>>> humanize.naturaltime(dt.timedelta(seconds=3))
   214‚Üí'3 seconds ago'
   215‚Üí```
   216‚Üí
   217‚ÜíYou can pass additional parameter `path` to `activate` to specify a path to search
   218‚Üílocales in.
   219‚Üí
   220‚Üí```pycon
   221‚Üí>>> import humanize
   222‚Üí>>> humanize.i18n.activate("xx_XX")
   223‚Üí<...>
   224‚ÜíFileNotFoundError: [Errno 2] No translation file found for domain: 'humanize'
   225‚Üí>>> humanize.i18n.activate("pt_BR", path="path/to/my/own/translation/")
   226‚Üí<gettext.GNUTranslations instance ...>
   227‚Üí```
   228‚Üí
   229‚Üí<!-- usage-end -->
   230‚Üí
   231‚ÜíHow to add new phrases to existing locale files:
   232‚Üí
   233‚Üí```sh
   234‚Üíxgettext --from-code=UTF-8 -o humanize.pot -k'_' -k'N_' -k'P_:1c,2' -k'NS_:1,2' -k'_ngettext:1,2' -l python src/humanize/*.py  # extract new phrases
   235‚Üímsgmerge -U src/humanize/locale/ru_RU/LC_MESSAGES/humanize.po humanize.pot # add them to locale files
   236‚Üí```
   237‚Üí
